name: Our Lady of the Vigil
description: @msergisonmain  - digital paining - The Conqueror Worm BY EDGAR ALLAN POE - "...Out—out are the lights—out all!       And, over each quivering form, The curtain, a funeral pall,    Comes down with the rush of a storm,    While the angels, all pallid and wan,       Uprising, unveiling, affirm That the play is the tragedy, “Man,”       And its hero, the Conqueror Worm."
